commit.message: travis: test on ubuntu 18.04 (#374)

Django 3.0 Support (#373)

* Add no-op wrapper for Django >= 3

* Add tox environments for Python 3.8, Django 3.0

* Add Python 3.8 to Travis config

* Correct conditional for Django version

* Simpler decorator in line with original from six

* Conditional imports of six in tests

Overrides six methods called in model tests

* Conditional expected error message

* Replace Unicode literal with escaped code point

Avoids having to declare file encoding in Python 2
Fix a few random docs typos
